name: exdown
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "exdown" %}
{% set version = "0.9.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: af44828a0914a4e89b6b83037fcd3e74b8ce8e3aee54d20b87fada59fbe35c0d

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - python >=3
    - pip
    - setuptools
  run:
    - python >=3
    - pytest

test:
  imports:
    - exdown
  requires:
    - pytest
  source_files:
    - tests/
  commands:
    - python -m pytest

about:
  home: https://github.com/nschloe/exdown
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt
  summary: Extract and test code blocks from Markdown

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - nschloe
